{"_id":"ZDaKhPkQ8xlnjGwP","name":"Héroïsme","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/life/heart-cross-strong-blue.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Vous imprégnez de courage une créature consentante que vous touchez. Jusqu'à la fin du sort, elle est immunisée contre l'état <em>terrorisé</em> et, au début de chacun de ses tours, elle gagne un nombre de points de vie temporaires égal à votre modificateur de caractéristique d'incantation. Quand le sort se termine, la cible perd les éventuels points de vie temporaires restants issus de ce sort.</p>\n<p><strong>À plus haut niveau</strong>. Si vous lancez ce sort en utilisant un emplacement de niveau 2 ou supérieur, vous pouvez affecter une créature de plus par niveau au-delà du niveau 1.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Manuel des règles","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature","range":{"value":"contact"}},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":null},"damage":{"parts":[["@mod","temphp"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"enc","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":true},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":true},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""},"spellType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"time":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"damageType":{"value":"","_deprecated":true},"concentration":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"ritual":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"prepared":{"value":null,"_deprecated":true},"price":0},"effects":[{"_id":"OePprJZRM7rAeBMh","changes":[{"key":"macro.actorUpdate","mode":0,"